                    ],
                    "message": {
                        "text": "Using multiple require statements is cheaper than using && multiple check combinations.  There are more advantages, such as easier to read code and better coverage reports."
                    },
                    "ruleId": "semgrep_1_131_0_1_2_1_use_multiple_require"
                },
                {
                    "locations": [
                        {
                            "physicalLocation": {
                                "artifactLocation": {
                                    "uri": "/home/ryan/Documents/LLM/Code/Qwen/SupplyChain_F.sol"
                                },
                                "region": {
                                    "startLine": 4180
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "message": {
                        "text": "Caching the array length outside a loop saves reading it on each iteration, as long as the array's length is not changed during the loop."
                    },
                    "ruleId": "semgrep_1_131_0_1_2_1_array_length_outside_loop"
                },
                {
                    "locations": [
                        {
                            "physicalLocation": {
                                "artifactLocation": {
                                    "uri": "/home/ryan/Documents/LLM/Code/Qwen/SupplyChain_F.sol"
                                },
                                "region": {
                                    "startLine": 4180
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "message": {
                        "text": "A lot of times there is no risk that the loop counter can overflow.  Using Solidity's unchecked block saves the overflow checks."
                    },
                    "ruleId": "semgrep_1_131_0_1_2_1_unnecessary_checked_arithmetic_in_loop"
                },
                {
                    "locations": [
                        {
                            "physicalLocation": {
                                "artifactLocation": {
